{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/flutter/flutter_6/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Devlog","author":"JonginPark","siteUrl":"https://SiverPineValley.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"SiverPineValley/devlog"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":""}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"f96a3b04-0f7f-5f1f-8642-9ba66a30f62e","excerpt":"1. 개요 flutter를 사용하다 보면 자주 마주하게 되는 에러들이 있다. 이러한 에러들에 대한 정리와, 이를 어떻게 처리하면 좋을지에 대해 정리해보았다. 2. 에러들의 종류 2.1. ProviderNotFound Error 앞서 자주 보게되었던 ProviderNotFound에러이다. 이 에러가 발생하는 케이스는 몇 가지 있는데, 다음과 같다. 첫 번째로는,\n새로운 Provider를 생성했음에도 Hot-restart를 하지 않았을 때 발생하는 에러이다. Hot-restart…","html":"<h1 id=\"1-개요\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%EA%B0%9C%EC%9A%94\" aria-label=\"1 개요 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 개요</h1>\n<p>flutter를 사용하다 보면 자주 마주하게 되는 에러들이 있다. 이러한 에러들에 대한 정리와, 이를 어떻게 처리하면 좋을지에 대해 정리해보았다.</p>\n</br>\n<h1 id=\"2-에러들의-종류\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%EC%97%90%EB%9F%AC%EB%93%A4%EC%9D%98-%EC%A2%85%EB%A5%98\" aria-label=\"2 에러들의 종류 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 에러들의 종류</h1>\n<h2 id=\"21-providernotfound-error\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#21-providernotfound-error\" aria-label=\"21 providernotfound error permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2.1. ProviderNotFound Error</h2>\n<div align=\"left\">\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 49.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"provider not found\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/0d9ce99a65dd08e32598d334a3619ebd/c1b63/provider_not_found.png\" srcset=\"/static/0d9ce99a65dd08e32598d334a3619ebd/5a46d/provider_not_found.png 300w,\n/static/0d9ce99a65dd08e32598d334a3619ebd/0a47e/provider_not_found.png 600w,\n/static/0d9ce99a65dd08e32598d334a3619ebd/c1b63/provider_not_found.png 1200w,\n/static/0d9ce99a65dd08e32598d334a3619ebd/d61c2/provider_not_found.png 1800w,\n/static/0d9ce99a65dd08e32598d334a3619ebd/97a96/provider_not_found.png 2400w,\n/static/0d9ce99a65dd08e32598d334a3619ebd/91a65/provider_not_found.png 2476w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n    </span>\n</div>\n</br>\n<p>앞서 자주 보게되었던 ProviderNotFound에러이다. 이 에러가 발생하는 케이스는 몇 가지 있는데, 다음과 같다.</p>\n</br>\n<p>첫 번째로는,\n새로운 Provider를 생성했음에도 Hot-restart를 하지 않았을 때 발생하는 에러이다. Hot-restart 후 확인하면 해결되는 문제이다.</p>\n</br>\n<p>두 번째로는, 잘못된 route로 발생하는 에러이다. Route 내에 정의된 Provider는 다른 route에서는 접근할 수 없는 유형으로, Provider를 보다 상단의 위젯에서 정의하거나, Builder 위젯을 사용하거나, ProxyProvider 등의 방법으로 해결할 수 있다.</p>\n</br>\n<p>마지막으로는, 잘못된 BuildContext를 사용했을 경우 발생할 수 있는 에러로 앞선 예제에서는 Provider를 감싼 Route 위젯의 context가 사용되거나 해서 발생하는 에러로 context를 사용하지 않도록 수정해주면 대부분 해결된다. 혹은, Provider의 생성 위치를 변경해주는 방법으로도 해결 가능하다.</p>\n</br>\n<h2 id=\"22-setstate-or-markneedsbuild-called-during-build\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#22-setstate-or-markneedsbuild-called-during-build\" aria-label=\"22 setstate or markneedsbuild called during build permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2.2. setState() or markNeedsBuild() called during build.</h2>\n<div align=\"left\">\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 44.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"set state mark need build\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/191569e618f4a49b304fa29b77b78995/c1b63/set_state_mark_need_build.png\" srcset=\"/static/191569e618f4a49b304fa29b77b78995/5a46d/set_state_mark_need_build.png 300w,\n/static/191569e618f4a49b304fa29b77b78995/0a47e/set_state_mark_need_build.png 600w,\n/static/191569e618f4a49b304fa29b77b78995/c1b63/set_state_mark_need_build.png 1200w,\n/static/191569e618f4a49b304fa29b77b78995/d61c2/set_state_mark_need_build.png 1800w,\n/static/191569e618f4a49b304fa29b77b78995/82e86/set_state_mark_need_build.png 1978w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n    </span>\n</div>\n</br>\n<p>위 에러는 framework가 위젯을 그리고 있는데, 다시 위젯을 그려달라는 요청이 들어왔을 때 발생한다. Stateful 위젯의 State 위젯 내에서 initState 중간에 Provider의 값을 변경하는 경우 발생할 수 있다. 이러한 에러가 발생하는 이유는 Provider에서 화면을 렌더링하는 절차를 살펴보면 알 수 있다.</p>\n</br>\n<ul>\n<li>화면 렌더링 절차</li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n<li>화면 구성 요소 생성 (BuildContext)</li>\n<li>initState</li>\n<li>didChangeDependencies</li>\n<li>Build</li>\n</ol>\n</br>\n<p>페이지가 빌드된 이후부터 우리는 다른 것들을 그릴 수 있게 되는데, initState의 경우 렌더링 중간에 진행되는 절차이므로, 해당 단계에서 context를 이용하여 다른 것들을 화면에 그리는 것이 불가능하다. 마찬가지로, 페이지에 무언가를 그리면서 다른 화면으로 이동시킬 때도 마찬가지로 발생할 수 있다.</p>\n</br>\n<p>이러한 케이스를 방지하기 위해 flutter 프레임워크에서는 자체적으로 해결할 수 있는 방안을 제공해준다. <code class=\"language-text\">addPostFrameCallback()</code> 함수이다.</p>\n</br>\n<h3 id=\"221-addpostframecallback\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#221-addpostframecallback\" aria-label=\"221 addpostframecallback permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2.2.1. addPostFrameCallback</h3>\n<div align=\"left\">\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 35.66666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"add post frame callback\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/eea69792edb8ebfaf1ffae73263a0d18/c1b63/add_post_frame_callback.png\" srcset=\"/static/eea69792edb8ebfaf1ffae73263a0d18/5a46d/add_post_frame_callback.png 300w,\n/static/eea69792edb8ebfaf1ffae73263a0d18/0a47e/add_post_frame_callback.png 600w,\n/static/eea69792edb8ebfaf1ffae73263a0d18/c1b63/add_post_frame_callback.png 1200w,\n/static/eea69792edb8ebfaf1ffae73263a0d18/d61c2/add_post_frame_callback.png 1800w,\n/static/eea69792edb8ebfaf1ffae73263a0d18/de9fe/add_post_frame_callback.png 2146w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n    </span>\n</div>\n</br>\n<p>이 함수의 역할을 화면이 렌더링 된 이후, 등록된 콜백을 실행시키는 역할이다. UI에 영향을 주는 행동을 현재 frame 이후로 지연시킨다.</p>\n</br>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"dart\"><pre class=\"language-dart\"><code class=\"language-dart\">  <span class=\"token metadata function\">@override</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">initState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">super</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">initState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token class-name\">WidgetsBinding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>instance<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addPostFrameCallback</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>_<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      context<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>read<span class=\"token generics\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Counter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">increment</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      myCounter <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> context<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>read<span class=\"token generics\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Counter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>counter <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n</br>\n<p>이와 유사한 또 다른 방법으로는 <code class=\"language-text\">Future.delayed(Duration)</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">Future.microtask()</code> 함수를 이용하는 방법이다.</p>\n</br>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"dart\"><pre class=\"language-dart\"><code class=\"language-dart\">  <span class=\"token metadata function\">@override</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">initState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">super</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">initState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token class-name\">Future.Delayed</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Duration</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>seconds<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      context<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>read<span class=\"token generics\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Counter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">increment</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      myCounter <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> context<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>read<span class=\"token generics\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Counter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>counter <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n</br>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"dart\"><pre class=\"language-dart\"><code class=\"language-dart\">  <span class=\"token metadata function\">@override</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">initState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">super</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">initState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token class-name\">Future</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">microtest</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      context<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>read<span class=\"token generics\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Counter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">increment</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      myCounter <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> context<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>read<span class=\"token generics\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Counter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>counter <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n</br>\n<h2 id=\"23-widget-트리-밖에서-provider-value를-listen했을-때\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#23-widget-%ED%8A%B8%EB%A6%AC-%EB%B0%96%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-provider-value%EB%A5%BC-listen%ED%96%88%EC%9D%84-%EB%95%8C\" aria-label=\"23 widget 트리 밖에서 provider value를 listen했을 때 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2.3. Widget 트리 밖에서 Provider value를 listen했을 때</h2>\n<div align=\"left\">\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 36.66666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"listen outside widget\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/3f4ac28b54879b6b59faa42bee9f8938/c1b63/listen_outside_widget.png\" srcset=\"/static/3f4ac28b54879b6b59faa42bee9f8938/5a46d/listen_outside_widget.png 300w,\n/static/3f4ac28b54879b6b59faa42bee9f8938/0a47e/listen_outside_widget.png 600w,\n/static/3f4ac28b54879b6b59faa42bee9f8938/c1b63/listen_outside_widget.png 1200w,\n/static/3f4ac28b54879b6b59faa42bee9f8938/d61c2/listen_outside_widget.png 1800w,\n/static/3f4ac28b54879b6b59faa42bee9f8938/82e86/listen_outside_widget.png 1978w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n    </span>\n</div>\n</br>\n<p>위 에러는 제목에서 설명한 대로, Widget 트리 밖에서 Provider value를 Listen하려 했을 때 발생한다. 즉, Build하는 위젯의 변경사항을 watch하는 것이 안된다는 뜻이다. 이를 해결하기 위해서는 <code class=\"language-text\">Provider.of</code> 함수의 listen 파라미터를 false로 주거나, <code class=\"language-text\">read</code> extension 함수를 사용하면 된다.</p>\n</br>\n<h2 id=\"24-의존성-있는-widget이-변경될-때-발생하는-에러\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#24-%EC%9D%98%EC%A1%B4%EC%84%B1-%EC%9E%88%EB%8A%94-widget%EC%9D%B4-%EB%B3%80%EA%B2%BD%EB%90%A0-%EB%95%8C-%EB%B0%9C%EC%83%9D%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EC%97%90%EB%9F%AC\" aria-label=\"24 의존성 있는 widget이 변경될 때 발생하는 에러 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2.4. 의존성 있는 Widget이 변경될 때 발생하는 에러</h2>\n<div align=\"left\">\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 36%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"dependent widget change\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/ad7026e41b98a0c3fe5f62f67028efcc/c1b63/dependent_widget_change.png\" srcset=\"/static/ad7026e41b98a0c3fe5f62f67028efcc/5a46d/dependent_widget_change.png 300w,\n/static/ad7026e41b98a0c3fe5f62f67028efcc/0a47e/dependent_widget_change.png 600w,\n/static/ad7026e41b98a0c3fe5f62f67028efcc/c1b63/dependent_widget_change.png 1200w,\n/static/ad7026e41b98a0c3fe5f62f67028efcc/d61c2/dependent_widget_change.png 1800w,\n/static/ad7026e41b98a0c3fe5f62f67028efcc/a6d66/dependent_widget_change.png 2070w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n    </span>\n</div>\n</br>\n<p>이 에러는 특정 위젯이 빌드되고 있는 시점에 다른 위젯을 그려달라고 요청 했을 때 발생한다. 위젯이 빌드되는 프로세스 중간 단계인 <code class=\"language-text\">initState()</code> 함수나 constructor 내에서 다른 위젯을 그려달라는 요청이 있을 때 발생할 수 있다. 마찬가지로, <code class=\"language-text\">addPostFrameCallback()</code> 함수로 파훼가 가능하다.</p>\n</br>\n<h2 id=\"25-빌드되는-중간에-widget을-그려달라고-했을-때\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#25-%EB%B9%8C%EB%93%9C%EB%90%98%EB%8A%94-%EC%A4%91%EA%B0%84%EC%97%90-widget%EC%9D%84-%EA%B7%B8%EB%A0%A4%EB%8B%AC%EB%9D%BC%EA%B3%A0-%ED%96%88%EC%9D%84-%EB%95%8C\" aria-label=\"25 빌드되는 중간에 widget을 그려달라고 했을 때 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2.5. 빌드되는 중간에 Widget을 그려달라고 했을 때</h2>\n<div align=\"left\">\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 36%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"set state mark need build 2\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/25ef418068659c988f0439ad929400c4/c1b63/set_state_mark_need_build_2.png\" srcset=\"/static/25ef418068659c988f0439ad929400c4/5a46d/set_state_mark_need_build_2.png 300w,\n/static/25ef418068659c988f0439ad929400c4/0a47e/set_state_mark_need_build_2.png 600w,\n/static/25ef418068659c988f0439ad929400c4/c1b63/set_state_mark_need_build_2.png 1200w,\n/static/25ef418068659c988f0439ad929400c4/d61c2/set_state_mark_need_build_2.png 1800w,\n/static/25ef418068659c988f0439ad929400c4/e53e8/set_state_mark_need_build_2.png 1982w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n    </span>\n</div>\n</br>\n<p>이전에 설명한 2.2의 케이스와 유사하게, 빌드되는 중간에 위젯의 값이 변경되어 다시 그려달라고 했을 때 발생하는 에러이다. 에러 내용이 조금 다른건 initState가 아닌, Build 함수의 return 이전에 호출했을 경우이다. 이 경우에도 역시 <code class=\"language-text\">addPostFrameCallback()</code> 함수를 사용하면 된다.</p>\n</br>\n<h1 id=\"3-출처\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%EC%B6%9C%EC%B2%98\" aria-label=\"3 출처 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. 출처</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.udemy.com/course/flutter-provider-essential-korean/\">https://www.udemy.com/course/flutter-provider-essential-korean/</a></br></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"[Flutter] 06. Provider에서 자주 마주치게 되는 에러들","date":"January 21, 2024"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/flutter/flutter_6/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/flutter/flutter_5/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[Flutter] 05. Proxy Provider"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/flutter/flutter_7/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[Flutter] 07. ChangeNotifier를 이용한 action 처리"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3128451518","643154061"],"slicesMap":{}}